Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:56.17,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}They will finally feel the flames
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:23:00.60,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}Flames that run down through my veins
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:04.94,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}I will make the city burn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:09.30,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}We're not planning to return
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:13.70,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}Trying so hard to be free
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:17.52,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}To make you see what I see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:22.43,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}Hold on to your wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:26.25,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}If you can't hold on to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:30.05,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}Forgive me for letting you down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:35.30,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}Forgive me for letting you down again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:38.50,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}I guess I'm not strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:42.34,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}Right now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:49.70,edd-english,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}Oh my love
