Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:56.17,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}他们终究会擦出爱情之火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:23:00.60,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}火化为血液 在我体内流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:04.94,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}我会引燃这座都市
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:09.30,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}我们从未有撤退的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:13.70,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}努力去获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:17.52,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}只为让你见我所见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:22.43,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}牢牢抓住你的期盼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:26.25,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}如果你无法再握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:30.05,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}请原谅我 让你失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:35.30,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}请原谅我 又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:38.50,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}我想还未拥有守护你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:42.34,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}只为此时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:49.70,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}哦 我的挚爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:54.03,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}我们永恒的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:24:01.32,edd-chs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur2\fad(150,350)}你我永不分离
